title: Nubrac got unbanned and he's currently destroying people in D1/Master
body:
Nubrac haters just got humiliated.
He got the top turret first as teemo support. Enemy fiora was down 45 cs, killed her in lane and totally zoned her.

GET REKT NUBRAC HATERS LOL
If the strategy doesn't work how did he win a game vs Sneaky and how he's winning now???
